## Lessons Learned

This scenario demonstrates how routine administrative actions can generate valuable security telemetry and highlights the importance of monitoring privileged activity, account management, and access to sensitive resources.

```text
Administrator Activity
         │
         ▼
sudo Execution
         │
         ▼
auth.log
         │
         ▼
Splunk Ingestion
         │
         ▼
Activity Classification
         │
         ▼
Investigation & Monitoring
```

The resulting detections provide visibility into behaviors commonly associated with privilege abuse, persistence, and post-compromise account management.
